<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">

    <title>BuildBooks - Construction Project Management</title>

    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/normalize.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/styles.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/5.15.3/css/all.min.css">

</head>

<body>
    <header>
        <h1>BuildBooks</h1>
        <p>Your Construction Project Management Solution</p>
    </header>

    <section class="hero">
        <h1>Effortlessly Manage Your Projects</h1>
        <p>BuildBooks is a comprehensive platform that helps handymen and construction companies keep track of their
            projects, estimates, finances, and more.</p>
        <a href="/signup" class="btn btn-primary">Get Started</a>
    </section>

    <section class="features">
        <div class="feature">
            <i class="fas fa-file-alt"></i>
            <h3>Create Estimates</h3>
            <p>Effortlessly generate accurate estimates for your customers, complete with project details and costs.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature">
            <i class="fas fa-chart-line"></i>
            <h3>Track Finances</h3>
            <p>Monitor project expenses, track income, and easily calculate your estimated profit or loss.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature">
            <i class="fas fa-lock"></i>
            <h3>Secure Data Handling</h3>
            <p>Rest assured that your project details, customer information, and financial data are kept secure and
                confidential.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature">
            <i class="fas fa-paint-brush"></i>
            <h3>Customization Options</h3>
            <p>Personalize your estimates, contracts, and other documents to reflect your unique style and branding.</p>
        </div>
    </section>



    <section class="signup">
        <h2>Start Your Journey with BuildBooks</h2>
        <form action="/signup" method="POST">
            <div class="form-group">
                <label for="name">Name</label>
                <input type="text" id="name" name="name" required>
            </div>
            <div class="form-group">
                <label for="email">Email</label>
                <input type="email" id="email" name="email" required>
            </div>
            <div class="form-group">
                <label for="password">Password</label>
                <input type="password" id="password" name="password" required>
            </div>
            <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary">Sign Up</button>
        </form>
    </section>

    <script src="https://kit.fontawesome.com/your-font-awesome-kit.js" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
</body>

</html>